| 🔴 High | No error handler (stack trace leakage) | Info disclosure |
| 🔴 High | No security headers | XSS, clickjacking |
| 🟠 Medium | No rate limiting | DoS / brute force |
| 🟠 Medium | No CORS configuration | Cross-origin attacks |
| 🟡 Low | No input validation | Injection (if extended) |
| 🟡 Low | `console.log` logging | Poor observability |

